{"id":180136,"type":2,"name":"贝贝熊","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/bb/ee/180136_yra90.jpg","summary":"故事围绕贝贝熊一家展开，这个家庭由熊爸爸、熊妈妈和一双儿女组成，就象我们很多普通的家庭。这个家庭和睦友爱，但在对子女的教育上也存在很多无法避免的问题。比如熊哥哥和熊妹妹啃指甲、怕黑、作噩梦、懒惰、不愿完成作业、乱花钱、见啥要啥、迷恋电视、不会与他人相处、爱吃零食、爱逞能等等。当父母发现了这些问题时，总是努力试图了解孩子们的感受，用他们容易接受的方式去引导，所有的教育都从点滴小事做起。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>小熊一族</li><li><span>话数: </span>30</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>1985-09-14</li><li><span>别名: </span>The Berenstain Bears</li><li><span>导演: </span>Buzz Potamkin</li><li><span>国家: </span>美国</li>","collection":{"collect":3,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"无","count":1},{"name":"童年","count":1},{"name":"TV","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":631626,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/631626","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":631627,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/631627","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":631628,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/631628","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":631629,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/631629","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":631630,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/631630","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":631631,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/631631","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":631632,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/631632","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":631633,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/631633","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":631634,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/631634","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"A